Package: MonalisR
Title: MonalisR: Handling of the MONALISA Database
Description: This package provides several possibilities to access    
    and handle data from the SOS Dabase MONALISA.    
    This database has been formed as a joint cooperation of       
    EURAC Research's institutes of Earth Observation and    
    Alpine Environment together with the    
    Free University of Bolzano and Research Centre Laimburg.    
    The Database contains several ground sampling datasets for    
    agricultural and alpine parameters and    
    is fully accessable with the hereby provided package.
Version: 0.2
Author: Mattia Rossi, Daniel Frisinghelli
Maintainer: Mattia Rossi <Mattia.Rossi@eurac.edu>
